    <briefdescription>
<para>Plugin loading mode configuration for hipDNN. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This file defines the plugin loading modes that control how hipDNN loads and manages execution engine plugins. Plugins provide the actual GPU kernel implementations for deep learning operations. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
